Communicated by:
ProMED
<promed@promedmail.org>

[It's very disturbing to see the return of violence against polio workers in Pakistan. And somewhat ironic to have it be a splinter group of the Taliban, simultaneous with a massive vaccination campaign in neighboring Afghanistan currently under Taliban rule. (see https://www.econotimes.com/Afghanistan-Health-ministry-launches-polio-vaccination-campaign-1623333).

For a map of Pakistan showing provinces and districts, see https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/pak215_pakistan_districts_v5_a0_20181203.pdf. - Mod.MPP

